- Used by: virtual shared memory (PRD #26)
- Used by: BlockLoad/BlockStore shared memory path (PRD #23)
- Uses: CUDA runtime API (`cudaDeviceGetAttribute`, `cudaFuncGetAttributes`, `cudaFuncSetAttribute`)

